Usage: get_via_pillars [-help] [-required] { -term <term|term> | -instterm <instTerm|pgInstTerm> }

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-instterm <instTerm|pgInstTerm>     # InstTerm name or pointer
                                    # ((instTerm|pgInstTerm), required)
-required                           # Return the required flag (bool, optional)
-term <term|term>                   # Term(cell name/term base_name) name or
                                    # pointer. ((term|term), required)